External knowledge: The fantasy points are calculated based on the following formulas:
- 0.1 point per rushing yard;
- 6 points per rushing touchdown;
- 0.1 point per receiving yard;
- 6 points per receiving touchdown;
- 0.04 point per passing yard;
- 4 points per passing touchdown;
- minus 2 points per interception;
- injured players receive 75% of their total fantasy points.

sql:
SELECT COUNT(*) 
FROM weeks 
WHERE season_id = 0;

SELECT league_id, COUNT(team_id) AS number_of_teams
FROM fantasy_teams
GROUP BY league_id;

SELECT player_id
FROM fantasy_team_rosters
WHERE roster_status = 'active';
